---
title: One-Pan Honey-Dijon Turkey Cheddar Melts with Creamy Coleslaw
description: Get ready to meet your favorite new turkey and cheese sandwich! You’ll whip up tangy-sweet honey mustard to slather on sourdough bread, layer on turkey and cheddar, griddle in butter until toasty and melty, and serve with creamy coleslaw. It's everything you love about a lunchtime classic, elevated to perfection by our lunch-loving chefs.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6761a323bdfa7f79d1f16a39-9873c9b6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6761a323bdfa7f79d1f16a39-en-US.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-honey-dijon-turkey-cheddar-melts-6761a323bdfa7f79d1f16a39
author: Sara Heilman
cuisine: North America
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 15 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 740 kcal
